'''罗马'''是美国[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[亞當斯縣_(俄亥俄州)|亚当斯县]][[格林镇区_(俄亥俄州)|格林镇区]]的一座城镇<ref group="注">在俄亥俄州，人口在五千人以下的城市称为Village，与其他地方的Village意思不同，故译为城镇而非乡村。{{cite web |url=http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/703.01 |title=Ohio Revised Code Section 703.01(A) |accessdate=2007-09-12 |archive-date=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718075908/http://codes.ohio.gov/orc/703.01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，位于[[俄亥俄河|俄亥俄河]]畔， [[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]时共有94人。

==地理==
罗马位于{{coord|38|39|51|N|83|22|50|W|type:city}} (38.664266, -83.380456).<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110102044750/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2011-01-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

根据美国人口调查局数据，皮布尔斯面积为{{convert|0.26|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，其中{{convert|0.23|sqmi|sqkm|2}}为陆地，{{convert|0.03|sqmi|sqkm|2}}为水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2013-01-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[52号美国国道|52号美国国道]]穿过罗马的北面。

==历史==
威廉·斯托特于1835年定居于此<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8HwUAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA423#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=A History of Adams County, Ohio: From Its Earliest Settlement to the Present Time | publisher=E B. Stivers | author=Evans, Nelson Wiley | year=1900 | pages=423 | access-date=2015-09-13 | archive-date=2014-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209103601/http://books.google.com/books?id=8HwUAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA423#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>，在正式命名为罗马前，这里被称为斯托特（Stout）<ref>{{gnis|1085488}}</ref>，及时目前位于罗马的邮局依然叫做斯托特邮局。<ref>{{gnis|1956293|Stout Post Office}}</ref>

